game.name: Doctor Helper
game.description:
This time you have got a unique fun opportunity that you can explore anytime you want! We have brought to you a brand new doctor game where you have to play the role of a doctor helper. Are you ready to try out this fun challenge? Join Doctor Helper and show off the world that you are skilled enough to assist a medical professional and make any surgical procedure a complete success! You will be provided with instructions to complete your game.

You are in the operation theatre with an experienced doctor who is operating a patient. Be careful and try to be attentive all the time to collect the medical equipment he seeks for during the surgery of his patient! Make sure to grab the right tools in order to avoid the mistakes in this one of the best html5 surgery games for girls. It will be amazing to play the role of a doctor assistant especially at that time when no one is there except you. 

Finishing a surgery will be in your hands now in this princess time-based surgical game! A kind of important series of operations is running in the emergency room and providing the wrong equipment to your doctor can make this operation fail. Try to hand him the medical tools at the right moments to accomplish this job successfully! Be fast to assist your doctor to complete this important surgery before time expires! Good luck to browse more fun doctor games on atmegame.com, no download required!
